## Q24. What is Dynamic autoscaling?
Dynamic autoscaling adjusts capacity in a host pool by powering ON/OFF and creating/deleting session hosts based on demand. It uses scaling plan, is only available in Azure, supported for pooled host pools, and cannot be used with Azure Automation or Logic Apps.
---
